Revision history for perl script mbtget

1.5.0 2014-10-30

     - Add IPv6 support.

1.4.3 2014-10-30

     - Change two's complement decoding.

1.4.2 2014-10-29

     - Add Makefile.PL for easy install on all perl platforms.

1.4.1 2014-10-29

     - Better response handling for malformed responses (see joswr1ght pull 
       request #1).

1.4.0 2014-07-23

     - Add "-2c" for set "two's complement" mode (neg. value) on reads regs.

1.3.0 2014-03-10
     - Comment and "-h" text is now in english.

1.2.0 2012-04-12

     - Changing headers for source code publication.

